		"description": "<p>As an action you may become a living shadow for 1 minute. As long as you are in dim light or darkness you have resistance to all damage except force and radiant, can take the hide action as a bonus action even without cover, and can move through solid objects as difficult terrain. If you end your turn in a solid object you are shunted to the nearest unoccupied space and take 1d10 force damage. Once you have used this ability you cannot do so again until you finish a long rest.</p>",
